title: 1969704 COST: 8 ERROR: invalid jump destination (PUSH1) 2  and PC 00001228: SSTORE GAS: 673 COST: 20000 ERROR: Out of gas

body:
This is intended behaviour: https://solidity.readthedocs.org/en/latest/contracts.html#fallback-function
The fallback function should only be used as a last resort to log that a contract has received ether and not as the default way to receive ether. If you want to do anything apart from just sending ether, you should not use `.send()`.
